Package: soc.ca
Title: Specific Correspondence Analysis for the Social Sciences
Description: Specific and class specific multiple correspondence
        analysis on survey-like data. Soc.ca is optimized to the needs
        of the social scientist and presents easily interpretable
        results in near publication ready quality.
URL: https://github.com/Rsoc/soc.ca
Version: 0.8.1
Maintainer: Anton Grau Larsen <agraul@ruc.dk>
